high_descs: Turn around and walk to the head of the bathtub, where the faucet is.
Pick up the bar of soap sitting below the towel.
Turn and move to the sink on the left of the bathtub.
Place the soap in the sink, wet it, and pick it back up.
Turn and walk to the middle of the bathtub.
Place the soap so it is standing vertically on the edge of the bathtub near the towel.
anns.task_desc: Place wet soap on the edge of the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the bath tub, turn left, walk straight to the counter
Grab bar of soap from the tub
Place soap in sink, turn on faucet, then turn off faucet, then grab soap
turn around, walk towards the bath tub
anns.task_desc: Put the bar of soap in the bath tub

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the bath tub
turn left and move towards the sink
pick up the sponge from the side of the sink and drop it in the sink
wet the sponge in the sink
turn right and head towards the sink
use the wet sponge to wipe of the stain on the sink
anns.task_desc: wipe off a stain on the sink using a wet sponge.
